latestPosts.caption:
Charul’s sangeet was everything glam ✨🤌🏻
She’s is the sweetest being ever, I am so grateful that she trusted me completely with her skin regiment and makeup and she absolutely loved it.

In a world where many artists hide real skin texture behind filters, I believe in celebrating real skin and real pores.

With the right techniques, smile lines and pores can definitely be softened, but not completely erased, and that’s the beauty of authenticity.

She was a little tired too, so we snuck in a quick neck massage, because glam should feel as good as it looks 💆‍♀️
